data.description: Amazing opportunity!!! Come view this beautiful modern open concept home with 4 bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms, 2 car garage, on a cul-de-sac lot.     Beautiful white kitchen with island & granite countertops, like new stainless-steel appliances and walk-in pantry. Separate room in the front of the home can be used as a formal dining/living room or office space. Large primary bedroom boasts a large walk-in closet, ensuite bathroom with double sink, separate shower & bathtub.       Refrigerator, washer & dryer and grill included. Smart Home Technology!!!      Quiet Community that offers a pool, kiddie splash area, playground and clubhouse with a low $650/yr association fee. Excellent location with easy access to I85 and HWY 129. Great school system.
